自2015年起，[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]在[[对伊斯兰国的军事打击|多国军事打击]]下节节败退，其在伊拉克境内西北部占领的土地也逐步被[[伊拉克军队|伊拉克政府军]]夺回。<ref name="yahoo"/><ref name="independent"/><ref name="cbs">{{cite news|url=http://newyork.cbslocal.com/2016/03/26/iraq-soccer-match-bombing/|title=29 Killed In Iraq Soccer Stadium Suicide Bombing; Officials Say ISIS Claims Responsibility|work=CBS|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331035509/http://newyork.cbslocal.com/2016/03/26/iraq-soccer-match-bombing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月24日，伊拉克军队在美军空袭的协助下发起攻击，意图夺回北部重镇[[摩苏尔|摩苏尔]]；爆炸发生之前不久，伊政府军刚宣布军队和[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]民兵已从伊斯兰国手中夺回[[安巴尔省|安巴尔省]]的库贝萨镇（{{lang|en|Kubeisa}}）。<ref name="cbs"/><ref name="163Sport">{{cite news|url=http://sports.163.com/16/0326/03/BJ27TI7700050FOH.html|title=伊拉克足球赛遭恐袭29人丧生 ISIS宣称对此负责|work=网易|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329093758/http://sports.163.com/16/0326/03/BJ27TI7700050FOH.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DW">{{cite news|url=http://www.dw.com/en/suicide-bomber-strikes-soccer-stadium-near-baghdad-killing-at-least-30/a-19143436|title=Suicide bomber strikes soccer stadium near Baghdad, killing at least 30|work=Deutsche Welle|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326134012/http://www.dw.com/en/suicide-bomber-strikes-soccer-stadium-near-baghdad-killing-at-least-30/a-19143436|dead-url=no}}</ref>与此同时，该组织在全球各地发动多起恐怖袭击作为回击。<ref name="nyt"/><ref name="independent"/>3月，伊斯兰国在伊拉克城镇[[希拉_(伊拉克)|希拉]]制造汽车炸弹袭击造成60人死亡；<ref name="reuters"/>在爆炸发生前三天的3月22日，伊斯兰国在[[比利时|比利时]]首都[[布鲁塞尔|布鲁塞尔]]制造了连环爆炸案，造成至少31人死亡。<ref name="163Sport"/><ref name="nyt"/>分析人士预计，该组织在土地失守的同时会在全球制造更多类似形式的袭击。<ref name="DW"/>

伊斯坎德里耶以[[什叶派|什叶派]]居民为主，位于首都巴格达和什叶派宗教圣城[[卡爾巴拉|卡爾巴拉]]之间，在巴格达以南40公里。此前伊斯兰国已多次在巴格达附近发动针对什叶派的袭击行动。<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35901358|title=Iraq violence: 'IS suicide attack' kills 29 in football match|work=BBC|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-03-27|archive-date=2018-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314184523/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-35901358|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.antiwar.com/2016/03/25/iraqi-mayor-among-30-killed-in-soccer-game-bomb-attack-by-isis/|title=Iraqi Mayor Among 30 Killed in Soccer Game Bomb Attack by ISIS|work=Antiwar|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-03-25|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328144607/http://news.antiwar.com/2016/03/25/iraqi-mayor-among-30-killed-in-soccer-game-bomb-attack-by-isis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊斯坎德里耶在[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]期间也曾多次遭到暴力袭击，被称作“死亡三角”。<ref name="CNN"/><ref name="BBC"/>

