[[UTC+3|当地时间]]2016年3月25日下午7:15，[[伊斯坎德里耶|伊斯坎德里耶]]附近村庄艾尔-艾斯利亚（{{lang|en|Al-Asriya}}）的一座小型足球场遭到炸弹袭击。爆炸发生时恰逢一场当地足球比赛刚刚结束，当地官员正在向获胜球队颁奖。<ref name="reuters">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-violence-idUSKCN0WR1CC|title=Suicide bomber kills 26, wounds 71 south of Baghdad: official|work=Reuters|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325203832/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-violence-idUSKCN0WR1CC|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="yahoo">{{cite news|url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/suicide-bomber-kills-25-south-baghdad-police-172305466.html|title=Iraq buries young victims of football pitch bomb carnage|work=Yahoo! News|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-27|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402024411/https://www.yahoo.com/news/suicide-bomber-kills-25-south-baghdad-police-172305466.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="independent">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/baghdad-suicide-attack-killed-in-iraqi-capital-a6952496.html|title=Baghdad suicide attack: Isis bomber kills at least 29 after football match near Iraqi capital|work=Independent|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325215738/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/baghdad-suicide-attack-killed-in-iraqi-capital-a6952496.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>球赛由伊拉克什叶派武装力量“{{le|正义联盟 (伊拉克)|Asa'ib Ahl al-Haq|正义联盟}}”赞助。这一组织与[[伊朗|伊朗]]有合作，在前线参与了打击伊斯兰国的行动。<ref name="nyt2">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/26/world/middleeast/iraq-isis-bombing.html|title=ISIS Suicide Bomber in Iraq Kills Dozens at Soccer Game|work=New York Times|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325213931/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/26/world/middleeast/iraq-isis-bombing.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

球赛结束后，在官员准备向球员颁奖时，袭击者身穿炸弹腰带，走进聚集的围观人群，引爆了身上的炸弹。<ref name="CNN">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/25/middleeast/iraq-violence/|title=ISIS claims suicide attack on Iraqi stadium that kills 25|work=CNN|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326190940/http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/25/middleeast/iraq-violence/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="yahoo"/>爆炸造成至少41人死亡，105人受伤。伤亡者中多是观看球赛的年轻人，其中17名死者是年龄在10-16岁之间的男孩。<ref name="yahoo"/><ref name="nyt"/><ref name="ABCAU">{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-03-26/football-pitch-suicide-attack-kills-30-south-of-baghdad/7277422|title=Iraq suicide attack: 30 killed at football match south of Baghdad|work=[[澳大利亚广播公司|ABC]]|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409021932/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-03-26/football-pitch-suicide-attack-kills-30-south-of-baghdad/7277422|dead-url=no}}</ref>现场血迹斑斑，球场设施也遭到损坏。<ref name="yahoo"/>伊斯坎德里耶市长艾哈迈德·沙卡尔（{{lang|en|Ahmed Shaker}}）本人伤势过重，送医后不治身亡。他的一名保镖和五名安保人员也在袭击中丧生。<ref name="yahoo"/>“正义联盟”的五名高级成员也在袭击中受伤。<ref name="nyt2"/>

爆炸后，伊斯兰国通过网络声称对袭击负责，而袭击者名为赛义夫拉·艾尔-安萨里（{{lang|en|Saifullah al-Ansari}}）。根据袭击者的照片来看，其年龄尚不满20岁。<ref name="ABCAU"/><ref name="DW"/>伊斯兰国同时宣称此次袭击的目标是什叶派武装分子。<ref name="nyt"/>

==反响==
爆炸发生后，巴比伦省宣布将哀悼三日。<ref name="yahoo"/>“正义联盟”在巴比伦省的领导人则表示这次袭击是对“正义联盟”的报复，伊斯兰国的目的是动摇人民对正义联盟的信任。<ref name="nyt2"/>联合国秘书长伊拉克事务特别代表扬·库比什（{{lang|en|Ján Kubiš}}）称袭击事件是“暴行”，“可憎行径应当受到最强烈的谴责”。<ref name="CNN"/>正在访问伊拉克的[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]以及[[美国国务院|美国国务院]]也谴责了袭击事件，并对遇难者表示哀悼。<ref name="yahoo"/><ref name="CNN"/><ref name="USAToday">{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2016/03/25/suicide-bomb-blast-kills-25-soccer-stadium-south-baghdad/82259240/|title=Islamic State claims suicide bombing of Iraqi soccer stadium; 29 dead|work=USA Today|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325234519/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2016/03/25/suicide-bomb-blast-kills-25-soccer-stadium-south-baghdad/82259240/|dead-url=no}}</ref>新上任的[[国际足联|国际足联]]-{zh-cn:主席;zh-hk:會長;zh-tw:會長;}-[[詹尼·因凡蒂诺|詹尼·因凡蒂诺]]提到“足球使人团结”，对足球比赛中发生袭击案表示痛心。[[亚足联|亚足联]]也谴责了伊斯兰国在足球比赛和体育场馆中发动袭击的“可耻暴行”。<ref name="yahoo"/>

